{"tid":264720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港再不求變 競爭力只剩五年","createTime":"2017-05-31T05:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T16:17:32.000Z","uid":117200,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ced27a87b24344dacbcadda817af09eb70ab09","tid":264720,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170531/56762612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170531%2F56762612&d=syoTitLUGbK4biM2OqKsmm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f60968fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170531%2F56762612&h=39d667a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170531/56762612</a><br />\n<br />\n香港回歸之年，梁定邦掌管證監會，回想九七前國際社會最緊張香港能否保持法治和市場質素，今日外地同行關心的卻是，中國崛起時，香港角色會否淡化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不少人將公司質素轉差，歸咎於港交所（388），認為它既肩負上市公司牟利責任，又有權審批新股上市，角色衝突下，利益壓倒原則。這制度源出英國，但倫敦交易所早於2000年已將上市審批權，轉移至監管機構。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁定邦承認，由於法例賦予港交所獨市交易所地位，面臨公司質素轉差，被詬病角色衝突亦是香港「自己做嘅死結」。日後若將市場再仔細分層，包括細分投資者和上市公司門檻等要求，才有望紓解，尤其面對內地積極拓展不同板塊（如新三板、戰略新興板等）吸引多元化公司上市，加上電子交易日盛，若香港再不求變，他憂慮競爭力<span style=\"color: red;\">只剩五至十年</span>。"},{"pid":"69063a635234b79507de288b84292a7247efcc3b","tid":264720,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"北上廣深 幾時超越香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定個時間 唔好得把死人口"},{"pid":"f4ebc04c535d56fcb946b8977ef7626affde3d74","tid":264720,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又吹大陸超越香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ea22c03e8a670cea9fea70e70a5f3d1ed163c4","tid":264720,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"782dc65c4e32183c15ea30f178ce95a8c9d6f168","tid":264720,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"快點超越我<br />\n<br />\n樓價咪又繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8977db5834d92ed65e7d34a3861e4fd7849b4e8","tid":264720,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"就係審批咁黑暗老千，先吸引到大鱷老千入錢嚟搵食。"},{"pid":"b05f6ee7d8fb2da40f691871b86849e7e72e74cf","tid":264720,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"全民炒樓 大把競爭"},{"pid":"35ccb1b9d2e91dd006c232357c42275835d970c4","tid":264720,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"快點超英超美吧，香港wfc"},{"pid":"b4833df5be038bcf68a29bd80489b03aa72417c7","tid":264720,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"快撚D超越啦<br />\n<br />\n全中國人去上海 北京走水貨啦"},{"pid":"fcebb2a70a46f2802bc4715ba2995b69ba92e984","tid":264720,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7adf7c48e37413d60d95ba46af64031f63cb8e2","tid":264720,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"聽咗十年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceca809a63490e429137a0a1fc0e1306de2ffeee","tid":264720,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"回歸前已經要講啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c3f0d8ea5b0138824ae2da06d61244ca184df172","tid":264720,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"實際上又係喎。<br />\n你香港。除左炒炒賣賣重有咩可以做.....<br />\n你全香港最有錢果班。有幾多係靠炒野炒返來?"},{"pid":"f2b73d4b456533329d1ab3ebb17cdd056dc38075","tid":264720,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"跟大陸一齊貪咪得囉"},{"pid":"5c7fed13558e30a792e82480b4168e8b08eef66d","tid":264720,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:25:43.000Z","msg":"香港本地人競爭力只剩5年"},{"pid":"f37bbc2210d2f0b7528290fbafbadc45cd45ef46","tid":264720,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"嘛又係政府搞成咁"},{"pid":"081c7c88e14bbfdab5adb8956c78be1db9a117e8","tid":264720,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9e36d52f44ebdfa0a6399ea336761535e694548","tid":264720,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe9bb1a7deec55d65c532a469159ae63f3e416f","tid":264720,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"香港競爭力好高<br />\n只係土生土長又無乜家底既香港人競爭力低姐"},{"pid":"ebb32f7dca83c92875c664a8802a5449dedcec33","tid":264720,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港競爭力好高<br />\n只係土生土長又無乜家底既香港人競爭力低姐</blockquote><br />\nagree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672db67878baf3921733f88ea2b17b6af55163a7","tid":264720,"uid":48139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n睇下港交所主席咩人黎<br />\n咪搞成咁"},{"pid":"cb2b743bd0f4aa6f1814ef22d5cf8ba597b5de76","tid":264720,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"一早玩完啦<br />\n<br />\n教育斷層都出現咗十幾年<br />\n<br />\n叻個啲去哂讀啲商業科<br />\n<br />\n廢個啲讀science 同engine<br />\n<br />\n早十年政府肯洗錢去玩生物科技同IT<br />\n<br />\n發咗十世啦, 香港唔係冇人材 係啲官On9又短視<br />\n<br />\n而家住後幾十年睇住新加坡騎住香港啦<br />\n<br />\n我當你而家學始搞科研  養到班人出嚟都十幾年後嘅事<br />\n<br />\n點追?  有料個啲香港搞科研個啲 都比香港嚇走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dfdb0950869e73235f5467170c131099366030","tid":264720,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港競爭力好高<br />\n只係土生土長又無乜家底既香港人競爭力低姐</blockquote><br />\n真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7a5247d466d5bbea9471841ae52b3351a4284f","tid":264720,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"特首全部都係中央任命，立法會建制派一向過半<br />\n關香港人鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正地放香港獨立再雙普選<br />\n香港就可以真正求變"},{"pid":"a5b2abdc920d7e8906d41f5d8424545bc88133fb","tid":264720,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"變做大陸競爭力就真係無曬競爭力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}